UNWTO General Assembly in pictures   
Sep 16, 2015 All photos Â© Christian del Rosario eTN   
The 21st UN World Tourism Organization (UNWTO) General Assembly is taking place in Medellin, Colombia. Here, we take a pictorial walk through some of the highlights so far, courtesy of photographer Christian del Rosario.
